title: Star Trek Regeneration (2011) - deLimited Productions Fanedit [7
description:
Summary: This edit of Star Trek: Generations is called "Regeneration" for several reasons. First there are the obvious and interesting orthographic links to the original "Generations" title. More important, one of the goals of Star Trek VII was to regenerate the movie franchise. Similarly, this version is an attempt to regenerate the story itself. The fan-editor does so by introducing significant changes to the film's beginning and controversial ending.

For more information about this work, visit the official project page: <a href="
